ssion could also originate from shock\nexcitation in the cavity walls of an envelope, but this requires an unusually\nhigh velocity of the wide-angle wind from T Tau N.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Jun 2008 20:13:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
