pha_s(M_Z) = 0.1180 \\pm 0.0008$. Our results are lower than previous values\nobtained from $\\tau$ decays.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 19 Jun 2008 09:35:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 29 Aug 2008 07:17:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-01-06"}
